<subSubSection id="C3776556EE473B23FC9AF904FC0AF8E9" pageId="278" pageNumber="279" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BD236DDEE473B23FC9AF904FC0AF8E9" blockId="278.[810,1452,1465,1832]" pageId="278" pageNumber="279">
<emphasis id="B919EACFEE473B23FC9AF904FC09F925" bold="true" box="[863,972,1738,1764]" pageId="278" pageNumber="279">Remarks</emphasis>
. The distinctive wing-like projections on the metasome have not been recorded previously in related genera.
</paragraph>
